üìù DESCRIPTION
------------------------------
ü§ñ Multi-Agent AI WhatsApp Bot for Service Businesses

Transform your salon/service business with this enterprise-level WhatsApp automation system featuring intelligent conversation routing, automated booking, and comprehensive business management.

How it works
Smart Intent Recognition** - AI automatically routes conversations to specialized agents
Complete Appointment Management** - Book, cancel, update appointments with calendar sync
Multi-Media Support** - Handles text, voice, images, and PDF documents
Rate Limiting & Spam Protection** - Professional 30 msg/hour limits with graceful UX
Automated 1-Day Reminders** - Sends WhatsApp reminders every evening for next-day appointments

Set up steps
WhatsApp Business API** setup (detailed instructions included)
Airtable Database** configuration (3 tables: Services, Bookings, Configuration)  
Google Calendar** integration for scheduling
Redis** for caching and conversation state
Gmail** for owner notifications
Configure business hours, services, and policies in Airtable

Key Features
5 Specialized AI Agents** (Booking, Cancellation, Updates, General Inquiry, Intent Recognition)
24-Hour Advance Reminders** - Automatic WhatsApp reminders sent at 8 PM for next day appointments
Double Booking Prevention** with real-time conflict detection
Conversation Memory** maintains context across interactions
Error Resilience** with backup models and graceful failure handling
Business Intelligence** with comprehensive logging and analytics
Professional UX** with natural conversation flow and emoji matching

Perfect for salons, spas, clinics, consulting services, or any appointment-based business. Includes complete setup documentation and business configuration templates.
